<type>(<scope>): <subject>

# type: feat|fix|refactor|perf|test|docs|build|ci|chore|style|revert
# scope: optional, English identifier such as core, graph, tauri, web, docs, ci
# subject: 中文优先，保留必要英文术语，不加句号，尽量不超过 72 个字符
# breaking change: add ! before :, for example <type>(<scope>)!: <subject>
#
# body: trivial/mechanical changes may omit the body
# body: substantive changes should explain why, what changed, risk/compatibility,
# body: and validation that was actually run
#
# footer: add issue refs or BREAKING CHANGE only when applicable
# BREAKING CHANGE: describe migration when needed
# Signed-off-by is required by default; use git commit -s
